      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PAW VINE (3) has a strong winning strike-rate here having won two of three starts. In the money last time at Warragul (26.12) in a Grade 4/5, finishing a 4 length second. Looks the one to beat with even luck. DADDY COOL (1) is a capable type and proved too strong last time to win by a nose at Bendigo in a handy 23.87 beating Paw Elodee. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. Looks a key chance if runs up to latest figure. AXIOMS (2) has a strong overall record having five wins and one places from nine starts but was out of the money last time when fifth (22.50) over 390m at Shepparton. Best form too dangerous to ignore. Have to include. PAW SHERMAN (7) should be thereabouts after filling a top-three spot most recently.",
